Executive: Ji, main keh raha tha sir, ek mail receive hua tha abhi aapki side se info@platinacables.com se ki kuch aapko email access karne mein kuch problems vagarah aa rahi hai?
Customer: Hain?
Executive: Ji, sir.

Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan ji, sir.

Customer: Hello.
